text: Musang sentheni may refer to: * 7.62×37mm Musang, a Filipino rifle cartridge * Gua Musang, a town and territory in Kelantan, Malaysia * Musang Berjanggut, Malaysian film * Anicca, the concept of impermanence in Buddhism ==See also== * The Asian palm civet, called musang in Tagalog, Malaysian and Indonesian.
title: Musang
